 * <i>user</i>,
 * <i>password</i>, <i>connect_timeout</i>,
 * <i>options</i>, <i>tty</i> (ignored), <i>sslmode</i>,
 * <i>requiressl</i> (deprecated in favor of <i>sslmode</i>), and
 * <i>service</i>. Which of these arguments exist depends
