 parameters" id="refsect1-function.pg-fetch-all-columns-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">result</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para"><span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.pgsql-result.php" class="classname">PgSql\Result</a></span> 实例，由<span class="function">{@link pg_query()}</span>、<span class="function">{@link pg_query_params()}</span> 或者 <span class="function">{@link pg_execute()}</span>（等）返回。</p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">field</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       Column number. Defaults to the first column if not specified.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.pg-fetch-all-columns-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   An <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.array.php" class="type array" style="color:#EAB766">array</a></span> with all values in the result column.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.pg-fetch-all-columns-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">result</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.pgsql-result.php" class="classname">PgSql\Result</a></span>  实例，之前接受 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div>  <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.pg-fetch-all-columns-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-2033">    