pan class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">row</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       在 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.pgsql-result.php" class="classname">PgSql\Result</a></span> 实例中将内部偏移量移动到的行。行号从零开始。      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.pg-result-seek-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   成功时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.true">true</a></span></strong>， 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.pg-result-seek-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">result</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.pgsql-result.php" class="classname">PgSql\Result</a></span>  实例，之前接受 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.pg-result-seek-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-2084">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>pg_result_seek()</strong></span> 示例</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 连接到数据库<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$conn </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_pconnect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"dbname=publisher"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 执行查询<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$result </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_query</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$conn</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"SELECT author, email FROM authors"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 寻找第三行（假设有 3 行）<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_result_seek</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$result</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">2</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 获取第三行记录<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$row </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_fetch_row</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$result</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br><br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.pg-result-seek-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link pg_fetch_row()} - 提取一行作为枚举数组</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link pg_fetch_assoc()} - 获取一行作为关联数组</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link pg_fetch_array()} - 获取一行作为数组</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link pg_fetch_object()} - 获取一行作为对象</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link pg_fetch_result()} - 从结果实例返回值</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
