></span></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   <span class="function"><strong>pg_lo_write()</strong></span> 在大对象的当前位置写入数据。  </p>  <p class="para">   要使用大对象接口，必须将其封装在一个事务块中。  </p>  <blockquote class="note" style="border:1px gray solid"><p><strong class="note" style="border:1px gray solid">注意</strong>:    </p><p class="para">    本函数以前的名字为 <span class="function"><strong>pg_lowrite()</strong></span>。   </p>  </blockquote> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-write-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">lob</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">通过 <span class="function">{@link pg_lo_open()}</span> 返回的 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.pgsql-lob.php" class="classname">PgSql\Lob</a></span> 实例。</p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">data</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       写入到大对象中的数据。如果 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">length</span> 是 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> 并且少于       <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">data</span> 的长度，仅会写入 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">length</span> 个字节。      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">length</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       可选的最大写入字节数。必须大于零且不大于 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">data</span> 的长度。默认为 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">data</span> 的长度。      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-write-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   写入到大对象的字节数，或出错时为 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-write-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">lob</span> 接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.pgsql-lob.php" class="classname">PgSql\Lob</a></span>   实例，之前接受 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>     <tr>      <td>8.0.0</td>      <td>       <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">length</span> 现在可为 null。      </td>     </tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-write-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-2067">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>pg_lo_write()</strong></span> 示例</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>   $doc_oid </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">189762345</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br>   </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$data </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"This will overwrite the start of the large object."</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br>   </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_connect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"dbname=jacarta"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>   </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_query</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"begin"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>   </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$handle </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_lo_open</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$doc_oid</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"w"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>   </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$data </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_lo_write</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$handle</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$data</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>   </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_query</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"commit"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-write-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link pg_lo_create()} - 新建大对象</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link pg_lo_open()} - 打开大对象</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
