an class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.pgsql-connection.php" class="classname">PgSql\Connection</a></span> 实例。</p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">visibility</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The required visibility: <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/pgsql.constants.php#constant.pgsql-show-context-never">PGSQL_SHOW_CONTEXT_NEVER</a></span></strong>,       <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/pgsql.constants.php#constant.pgsql-show-context-errors">PGSQL_SHOW_CONTEXT_ERRORS</a></span></strong>       or <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/pgsql.constants.php#constant.pgsql-show-context-always">PGSQL_SHOW_CONTEXT_ALWAYS</a></span></strong>.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.pg-set-error-context-visibility-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   The previous visibility level: <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/pgsql.constants.php#constant.pgsql-show-context-never">PGSQL_SHOW_CONTEXT_NEVER</a></span></strong>,   <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/pgsql.constants.php#constant.pgsql-show-context-errors">PGSQL_SHOW_CONTEXT_ERRORS</a></span></strong>   or <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/pgsql.constants.php#constant.pgsql-show-context-always">PGSQL_SHOW_CONTEXT_ALWAYS</a></span></strong>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.pg-set-error-context-visibility-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <div class="example" id="function.pg-set-error-context-visibility.example.basic">   <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>pg_set_error_context_visibility()</strong></span> example</strong></p>   <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9